description: This Chainlink VRF top 9% rating Gatinho purrs with a rating of 76, and a multiplier of 1x. It has a total score of 76, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 2 for North, 8 for East, 1 for South, and Nine Lives for West. Gatinho has the personality suit of punter. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/50761-28192-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Gatinho [76 Votes, Top 9% Rating]
